\dot{x}=x-y-x(x^2+y^2)+\frac{xy}{\sqrt{x^2+y^2}} \\ \dot{y}=x+y-y(x^2+y^2)-\frac{x^2}{\sqrt{x^2+y^2}}
r^2=x^2+y^2
